Done. Opened [PR #581](https://github.com/jdx/fnox/pull/581) and replied to [discussion #577](https://github.com/jdx/fnox/discussions/577#discussioncomment-17501928).

The fix makes `fnox daemon clear` clear every running fnox daemon socket, so profile-scoped caches get cleared together. I also added a regression test for default + `dev` profile caches and tightened daemon test teardown.

Verified with:

- `mise run build`
- `test/bats/bin/bats test/daemon.bats`
- `mise run test:cargo`
- `mise run lint`

